title: BRIEF-Newell Brands Confirms Receipt Of Starboard Value's Director Nominations

organizations.name: brief-newell brands confirms receipt of starboard value

text:
36 AM / Updated 6 minutes ago BRIEF-Newell Brands Confirms Receipt Of Starboard Value's Director Nominations   Newell Brands Inc: 
* NEWELL BRANDS CONFIRMS RECEIPT OF STARBOARD VALUE’S DIRECTOR NOMINATIONS 
* NEWELL BRANDS INC - ‍CONFIRMED THAT IT HAS RECEIVED NOTICE FROM STARBOARD VALUE AND OPPORTUNITY MASTER FUND LTD​ 
* NEWELL BRANDS - ‍RECEIVED NOTICE OF INTENTION TO NOMINATE 10 CANDIDATES TO STAND FOR ELECTION TO NEWELL BRANDS BOARD AT 2018 MEETING OF SHAREHOLDERS​
